You‚Äôre asking for a 5-year forecast (2025 ‚Üí 2030) using Best / Worst / Base scenarios ‚Äî the classic forward-looking planning view.

That means:

    Base case ‚Üí project median site totals forward (the ‚Äúmost likely‚Äù trajectory).

    Best case ‚Üí extend the historical highs (traffic recovery / optimistic).

    Worst case ‚Üí extend the historical lows (further erosion / pessimistic).

