    Typical month median ‚âà 10,849

    August median ‚âà 10,475

Now the difference is:
10,475‚àí10,84910,849√ó100‚âà‚àí3.5%
10,84910,475‚àí10,849‚Äã√ó100‚âà‚àí3.5%

That‚Äôs the real, defensible number.
